        <item>
            <title>
                <![CDATA[2024 Swift 學生挑戰賽開啓報名，50 名傑出獲獎者將獲邀參觀蘋果總部]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p data-vmark="5da7"><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT 之家</a> 2 月 6 日消息，蘋果今日宣佈開啓 2024 Swift 學生挑戰賽的報名通道。作為一項鼓勵學生開發者創新的全球性賽事，蘋果表示：「我們很榮幸能通過 Swift 學生挑戰賽支持和培養下一代開發人員、創意工作者和企業家。」</p><p style="text-align: center;" data-vmark="d29b"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/2/b16b3840-d292-4321-8d59-e35ab5a5e3be.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1500" h="750" data-advance="W3siVHlwZSI6IndlYnAiLCJVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL2ltZy5pdGhvbWUuY29tL25ld3N1cGxvYWRmaWxlcy8yMDI0LzIvN2M1MmRjMTQtMjVkZC00YTdkLTkyMWUtNzM3NmQ4MGM3MDZlLndlYnAifV0=" title="2024 Swift 學生挑戰賽開啓報名，50 名傑出獲獎者將獲邀參觀蘋果總部" width="1500" height="410" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="c0dd">據 IT 之家瞭解，挑戰賽鼓勵學生利用 App Playgrounds 開發應用程序，展示他們的創意和編程能力。這些作品不僅可以解決實際問題，更能幫助學生獲得未來職業所需的技能。</p><p data-vmark="d510">對 Swift 學生挑戰賽感興趣的學生可以登錄<a href="https://redirect.viglink.com/?format=go&amp;jsonp=vglnk_170717546478312&amp;key=c1c7d488bb2df8a8b659d5d41634d304&amp;libId=ls9jxvwn010023dg000UL1ohhofmz14652&amp;loc=https%3A%2F%2F9to5mac.com%2F2024%2F02%2F05%2F2024-swift-student-challenge%2F&amp;gppConsent=DBABBg~BUoAAAA&amp;ccpaConsent=1YNN&amp;v=1&amp;out=https%3A%2F%2Fdeveloper.apple.com%2Fswift-student-challenge%2F%3Fcid%3Dapple-newsroom&amp;title=Apple%20opens%202024%20Swift%20Student%20Challenge%20applications%20with%20new%20%27Distinguished%20Winners%27%20category%20-%209to5Mac&amp;txt=Apple%E2%80%99s%20developer%20website" target="_blank">蘋果開發者網站</a>註冊報名，報名通道將在未來三週內開放。最終將選出 350 名獲獎者，其中 50 名錶現出色的「傑出獲獎者」將獲邀於明年夏天前往蘋果總部園區參觀交流。所有獲獎者都將獲得一年期的蘋果開發者計劃會員資格、一份免費參加 Swift 應用開發認證考試的優惠券以及一份來自蘋果的特別禮物。</p><blockquote><p data-vmark="6643">今年的挑戰賽新增了「傑出獲獎者」類別，將在 350 名獲獎者中選出 50 位表現最為出色的學生，並邀請他們前往庫比蒂諾的蘋果總部參加獨家體驗活動。所有獲獎者都將獲得一年期的蘋果開發者計劃會員資格、一份免費參加 Swift 應用開發認證考試的優惠券以及一份來自蘋果的特別禮物。</p></blockquote><p data-vmark="03db">有關<a href="https://redirect.viglink.com/?format=go&amp;jsonp=vglnk_170717549691816&amp;key=c1c7d488bb2df8a8b659d5d41634d304&amp;libId=ls9jxvwn010023dg000UL1ohhofmz14652&amp;loc=https%3A%2F%2F9to5mac.com%2F2024%2F02%2F05%2F2024-swift-student-challenge%2F&amp;gppConsent=DBABBg~BUoAAAA&amp;ccpaConsent=1YNN&amp;v=1&amp;out=https%3A%2F%2Fdeveloper.apple.com%2Fswift-student-challenge%2Feligibility%2F&amp;title=Apple%20opens%202024%20Swift%20Student%20Challenge%20applications%20with%20new%20%27Distinguished%20Winners%27%20category%20-%209to5Mac&amp;txt=on%20Apple%E2%80%99s%20website" target="_blank">參賽資格要求</a>和<a href="https://redirect.viglink.com/?format=go&amp;jsonp=vglnk_170717550667118&amp;key=c1c7d488bb2df8a8b659d5d41634d304&amp;libId=ls9jxvwn010023dg000UL1ohhofmz14652&amp;loc=https%3A%2F%2F9to5mac.com%2F2024%2F02%2F05%2F2024-swift-student-challenge%2F&amp;gppConsent=DBABBg~BUoAAAA&amp;ccpaConsent=1YNN&amp;v=1&amp;out=https%3A%2F%2Fdeveloper.apple.com%2Fswift-student-challenge%2Fget-ready%2F&amp;title=Apple%20opens%202024%20Swift%20Student%20Challenge%20applications%20with%20new%20%27Distinguished%20Winners%27%20category%20-%209to5Mac&amp;txt=learning%20resources%20for%20students" target="_blank">學習資源</a>的詳細信息，請訪問蘋果開發者網站。</p><p class="ad-tips">廣告聲明：文內含有的對外跳轉鏈接（包括不限於超鏈接、二維碼、口令等形式），用於傳遞更多信息，節省甄選時間，結果僅供參考，IT 之家所有文章均包含本聲明。</p>
        ]]>
